What is RuckTrack?
------------------

RuckTrack is a free GPS file analyzing program, allowing to review routes tracked via GPS. It features GoogleMaps integration, graphs, statistics and capabilities for automatically correcting elevation information via SRTM data.


Requirements
------------

* Qt4 SDK
* libgdal



Building
--------

See INSTALL for information on how to build RuckTrack.



